{"tid":593736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消委會：「快的打車DiDi」讀取聯絡資料、相片、記憶卡　Call的App私隱權限過大 讚好此文:","createTime":"2018-03-15T08:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T13:57:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb5f193b6ba23117c4cff4ab6e2dc8d088ef714","tid":593736,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:48:59.000Z","msg":"手機往往儲存不少用家的個人資料，如果用家在安裝應用程式時，沒有仔細留意程式索取的權限，就有可能造成資料外洩。據消委會針對 7 個的士應用程式所做的測試，結果發現大部分網約的士應用程式，都向用家索取與服務無關的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/1-33-694x521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F1-33-694x521.jpg&h=de0e8db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據消委會調查發現， 7 個應用程式都要求授權，取得用家資料。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當中大部分應用程式，更向用家索取與網約的士服務無關的資料。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其中，前身為「快的打車」的「DiDi」需要最多權限，<strong><ins>包括讀取及修改記憶卡內容，取得相片、聯絡人資料及通話記錄、<ins>不通知用家自行下載檔案，以及控制閃光燈及使</ins>用麥克風</ins></strong>。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而「飛的」僅要求取得以 GPS 及網絡為基準的位置資料，是 7 個應用程式中索取最少權限，消委會指，這樣顯示營運商並不需要大量用家個人資料，亦可以提供有效的網約的士服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/11-2-694x278.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F11-2-694x278.png&h=ded015d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n消委會表示，向用家授權獲得過多資料及權限，都是侵犯私隱的行為，更有可能導致個人資料外洩。因此，消委會敦促各個應用程式營運商，應清楚列明服務所需的資料及權限，並避免索取過多資料。而消費者在下載應用程式時，亦應該詳細比較各個平台的所需權限，保護個人資料及私隱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：消委會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/15/taxi-app-too-much-power/tech-secure/?utm-medium=push-click&amp;utm-source=push-notification\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2Ftaxi-app-too-much-power%2Ftech-secure%2F%3Futm-medium%3Dpush-click%26utm-source%3Dpush-notification&d=TJ3MZuC4%2BvlQOXGaWtZ5AQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=e80e396e\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/15/taxi-app-too-much-power/tech-secure/?utm-medium=push-click&amp;utm-source=push-notification</a>"},{"pid":"ae8a8498fa355a3e8999ead9ebbc02897610e8c2","tid":593736,"uid":89514,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:00:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"053dc86ea8ec5f0e1ecc823775c2c07c6f2b1bb5","tid":593736,"uid":16161,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:27:33.000Z","msg":"一直用開飛的，真心方便好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee5409e2c7f338497df7b7b1fb0561fcad84e09","tid":593736,"uid":7688,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"即時剷淨飛的"},{"pid":"a8569076a95adb133c4167534d4899c659d4f145","tid":593736,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053dc86ea8ec5f0e1ecc823775c2c07c6f2b1bb5","tid":593736,"uid":16161,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:27:33.000Z","msg":"一直用開飛的，真心方便好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa1a6aaa40d705c53f970d5819d5aea34cf372b","tid":593736,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b95e4d04157122dbe34115a8a54efe12cba4ec","tid":593736,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"點解要叫didi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa13469eb63146ea191fb6018ff15e17bb2b4fd","tid":593736,"uid":50988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:43:32.000Z","msg":"有名你叫 &ldquo;打車&rdquo; 都仲要install嘅<br />\n就無得怪人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 